To get to know (something or someone)       | kennismaken
What is your name?                          | wat is je naam?
What is your name? (how are you called?)    | hoe heet je?
Who are you?                                | wie ben jij?
I'm (called) Peter                          | ik heet Peter
My name is Uni                              | mijn naam is Uni
Which country are you from                  | uit welk land kom je
Where do you come from?                     | Waar kom jij vandaan?
Where do you live?                          | Waar woon je?
I live in ..                                | Ik woon in
I come from Hungary                         | ik kom out Hongharije
My birthplace is Germany                    | Mijn geboorteland is Dutisland
How nice!                                   | Wat leuk!
And you?                                    | en jij?
What is your telefon number?                | Wat is je telefoonnummer?